data.description: This beautifully renovated 3 bedroom 2 bathroom Cape located in the Haven Section of South Edison constitutes the epitome of modern comfort and convenience. Brand new roof, windows, driveway, kitchen, bathrooms, floors, plumbing, electric, HVAC, furnace, water heater, and fence will provide the new owner peace of mind for many years to come. The first floor boasts 2 bedrooms, full bathroom, spacious and bright living room, a well-appointed kitchen with granite countertops. The second floor offers a beautiful, open and airy primary bedroom suite with a half bathroom, and a separate office/den/playroom space. The full basement provides 2 separate areas with so many possibilities. The finished part would make a perfect gym, home office, family room or storage area plus there is plenty of space in the utility room. There is a separate outside entrance leading to the basement as well as an inside one directly from the kitchen. The spectacular fully fenced-in backyard is an ideal canvas for relaxation and hosting gatherings. Excellent schools and location. Great commute to NYC with quick access to the Edison train station, major highways, including Rt 18, 1, Turnpike and Parkway. Close to grocery stores, restaurants, and entertainment. Nothing needs to be done. Just move in, unpack, and enjoy!
